Please follow the below steps,

&nbsp; &nbsp; 1. Click on "Articles" icon from "Site Manager".

&nbsp; &nbsp; 2. Click "edit" on any article.

&nbsp; &nbsp; 3. Click on any PageDesigner.

&nbsp; &nbsp; 4. Click on image icon as shown in below screenshot.

&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; https://i.snipboard.io/OCKGWD.jpg

&nbsp; &nbsp; 5. It will open popup screen having three fields including image caption and image alignment. See below screenshot,

&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; https://i.snipboard.io/3s6dtS.jpg

&nbsp; &nbsp; 6. Please upload image, write caption and choose alignment as per requirement.

&nbsp; &nbsp; 7. Click on "Upload" and it will generate the code that you can place in your article.

Please let us know how it works.

Thank you.
